snippet.title: [DEMO] SMB - Raiders of the Painting Realms NCFC 2008
snippet.description:
Welcome.

This video shows some of the gameplay elements you can expect from my fangame, Super Mario Bros. - Raiders of the Painting Realms.

This video is using characters and concepts by Nintendo and [edit] NO [/edit] music from the Dropkick Murphies without their permission, but I do not profit from making this.
